channel.title: Started with eclipse
channel.description:
Hello i've just started with eclipse, but im having trouble understanding how to use it, for sure for the errors it gives.
So im looking for some1 who has a few minutes free to help me out, just setting it up and explain me how to use it for my 317 source.
If u want to help me, you can do it by skype (sharescreen) or teamviewer.
my skype : nielskeeeeeeeen
